<p rend="chapter">Kiyādayo</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="118"><hi rend="paranum">118</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Kī vinimaye ci caye ji jaye ñā’vabodhane,</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Thava’bhitthave kampane dhu (atho) pu pavane (siyā;)</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="119"><hi rend="paranum">119</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1">Pī tappaṇe mā pamāṇe khipakkhepe mi hiṃsane,</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Mi pamāṇe mu bandhe (ca) lu pacchede si bandhane</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Asa bhakkhaṇe (atho) gaha upādāne (kiyādayo;)</p>
